Dolores Gray https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dolores_Gray 0 Dolores Gray (June 7, 1924 – June 26, 2002) was an American actress and singer. She was nominated for the Tony Award for Best Lead Actress in a Musical twice, winning once. Dolores_Gray ( June_7_,_1924 – June_26_,_2002 ) was an_American_actress_and_singer .
